text: Malaya Sosnova () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bolshesosnovskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 360 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == Geography == It is located 6.5 km south-east from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Malaya Sosnova
